# AI-Assisted Journal System - Frontend

This is the frontend application for the AI-Assisted Journal System, built with React.

## Features

- ✍️ Write journal entries with nature ambience selection
- 🔍 Real-time emotion analysis using AI
- 📖 View all past journal entries
- 📊 See insights about emotional patterns over time

## Prerequisites

- Node.js (v14 or higher)
- npm or yarn

## Installation

1. Install dependencies:
```bash
npm install